contentrichtext.text: '''Venter''' is a surname, and may refer to: * [[Brendan Venter]] (1969–), [[Rugby union]] footballer * [[Christoffel Venter]] (1892–1977), [[South African]] military commander * [[Craig Venter]] (1946–), [[United States|American]] [[biologist]] and businessman * [[Dora Venter]] (1976-), [[Hungary|Hungarian]] [[pornographic film actress]] * [[Jacobus Johannes Venter]] (1814–1889), [[South African]] [[Boer]] [[political figure]] ==See also== * [[Abdomen]] – the term '''venter''' may refer to the [[ventral]] side of an animal or plant organ. * ''Venter'', the [[Hungarian language|Hungarian]] name for Vintere village, [[Holod, Bihor|Holod]] Commune, Bihor County, Romania <!-- It does not help to add disambig or hndis tags where the page only contains people who share a surname --> {{surname}}
